  <text>
    <front>
      <note type="annotation">
                <p rend="left" xml:id="K_5736_p1">
                    <lb xml:id="p1-l1"/>
        <hi rend="underline">riservatissima</hi>
      </p> </note>
      <div type="printedheader">
        <p rend="left" xml:id="K_5736_p2">
                    <lb xml:id="p1-l2"/>
          <fw>CABINETTO DEL SINDACO</fw>
        </p>
      </div>
      <div type="dateline">
        <p rend="right" xml:id="K_5736_p3">
                    <lb xml:id="p1-l3"/>
          <placeName type="place" key="Genua (I)">Genova</placeName>
          <lb xml:id="p1-l4"/>
          <hi rend="underline">
            <date when="1870-05-08">8 Maggio 1870</date>
                    </hi>
        </p>
      </div>
      <div type="address">
        <p rend="center" xml:id="K_5736_p4">
                    <lb xml:id="p1-l5"/>
          <choice>
                        <abbr>Sig.</abbr>
                        <expan>Signore (Herr)</expan>
                    </choice> Escher
        <lb xml:id="p1-l6"/>Presidente del
        <lb xml:id="p1-l7"/>Comitato <placeName type="place" key="St. Gotthard (Pass)">Gottardista</placeName> <lb xml:id="p1-l8"/>
                    <hi rend="underline">
                        <placeName type="place" key="Zürich (Stadt)">Zurigo</placeName>
                    </hi>
                </p>
      </div>
    </front>
    <body>
            <div>
      <p rend="indent" xml:id="K_5736_p5">
                    <lb xml:id="p1-l9"/>Mentre a moi parere le
        
<lb xml:id="p1-l10"/>cose di <placeName type="place" key="St. Gotthard (Pass)">Gottardo</placeName> procedono innanzi
        
<lb xml:id="p1-l11"/>assai bene, i nemici di questo
        
<lb xml:id="p1-l12"/>valico fanno naturalmente
        
<lb xml:id="p1-l13"/>con crescente intensità sempre
        
<lb xml:id="p1-l14"/>i più grandi sforzi in contrario.
</p>
      <p rend="indent" xml:id="K_5736_p6">
                    <lb xml:id="p1-l15"/>Coll`ultimo mio telegramma
        
    <lb xml:id="p1-l16"/>io avvisava di ciò la <choice>
                        <abbr>S. V. Ill<supplied>ustrissi</supplied>ma</abbr>
                        <expan>Signoria Vostra Illustrissima (Euer Hochwohlgeboren)</expan>
                    </choice> </p>
      <p rend="indent" xml:id="K_5736_p7">
                    <lb xml:id="p1-l17"/>Ora credo bene nell`interesse
        
<lb xml:id="p1-l18"/>dell`opera nostra di avvertire
        
     <lb xml:id="p1-l19"/>la <choice>
                        <abbr>S. V. Ill<supplied>ustrissi</supplied>ma</abbr>
                        <expan>Signoria Vostra Illustrissima (Euer Hochwohlgeboren)</expan>
                    </choice>, che il gruppo <placeName type="place" key="Mailand (I)">Mila<lb break="no" xml:id="p1-l20"/>nese</placeName>, composto in gran parte di
        
<lb xml:id="p1-l21"/>uomini d'affari e di costruttori,
        
<lb xml:id="p1-l22"/>è, sia per influenza materiale,

<lb xml:id="p1-l23"/>sia per influenza morale, un
        
<lb xml:id="p1-l24"/>utilissimo corporatore nostro in
        
<lb xml:id="p1-l25"/>
                    <placeName type="place" key="Italien (Königreich)">Italia</placeName>, che conviene averlo
        
<lb xml:id="p1-l26"/>consenziente ed interessato a
<lb xml:id="p1-l27"/>promuovere l'intrapresa del
        
<lb xml:id="p1-l28"/>
                    <placeName type="place" key="St. Gotthard (Pass)">Gottardo</placeName> –
</p>
      <p rend="indent" xml:id="K_5736_p8">
                    <lb xml:id="p1-l29"/>Io avverto di ciò la <choice>
                        <abbr>S. V. Ill<supplied>ustrissi</supplied>ma</abbr>
                        <expan>Signoria Vostra Illustrissima (Euer Hochwohlgeboren)</expan>
                    </choice> <lb xml:id="p1-l30"/>come di cose avrai importante
        

<pb n="2"/>
                    <lb xml:id="p2-l1"/>per quelle disposizioni,
        
<lb xml:id="p2-l2"/>concerti ch'Ella anderà conve<lb break="no" xml:id="p2-l3"/>niente promuovere del di

        
	<lb xml:id="p2-l4"/>Lei Comitato.</p>
    </div>
        </body>
    <back>
      <div type="closer">
        <p rend="indent" xml:id="K_5736_p9">
                    <lb xml:id="p2-l5"/>E me le ripeto</p>
        <p rend="right" xml:id="K_5736_p10">
                    <lb xml:id="p2-l6"/>
Devotissimo</p>
      </div>
